Quest:Alone in the Dark

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Million Years in the Making
Break Stuff (access quest)

Given By: Kachiri Fire Cloud

Giver Location: Cenote
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Defeat 2 Thunder Horn Zombies
Talk to Kachiri Fire Cloud
Hand In: Kachiri Fire Cloud

Reward:

355
20,555
Sabertooth
Avenging Fossil
Sun Serpent
Lord of Winter
Spinysaur
Celestial Calendar
Storm Owl

Leads to:

None

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to Alone in the Dark should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to Alone in the Dark in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
